name: Divya Chowdhary
title: Account Executive & Strategic Growth Specialist
summary: Award-winning Account Management professional driving revenue excellence within the cybersecurity and B2B technology sectors. Proven expert in generating £200K+ ACV and achieving 160% of quota through consultative engagement. specialized in bridging complex technical security needs with C-level business objectives to secure enterprise growth.

experience.description: Managed strategic MidMarket portfolio achieving £200K+ ACV (160% of quota). Orchestrated complex 6-stakeholder negotiations for £85K multi-year managed SOC & EDR contracts. Maintained 3.25:1 pipeline coverage and collaborated cross-functionally to reduce sales cycles from 65 to 48 days.

Grew partnership portfolio by 53% (valued at £350K) through prospecting multinationals including Microsoft and Deloitte. Ranked #3 of 18 nationally, achieving a 29% win rate against a 15% average. Promoted to Team Lead, coaching an 8-person team to increase pipeline generation by 65%.

projects.title: Enterprise Security Transformation
projects.description: Led a complex multi-year negotiation for an £85K Managed SOC + EDR contract. Established executive quarterly check-ins that generated a £45K+ expansion pipeline for Cloud Security services.

projects.title: Global Partnership Portfolio Growth
projects.description: Executed a high-volume prospecting strategy (900+ activities) to secure partnerships with global giants like Microsoft and IBM, maintaining a 90% retention rate across active accounts.
